to the scribe .vj.d. onely. And of goods
aboue the value of a C.s. vnto .xi. pounde,
iij.s.vj.d: And the Scribe to haue .xij.d. of
the summe. And for the probate of a Testament
of goods aboue the value of .xl.l'.v.s:
whereof the Scribe to haue .ij.s.vj.d. or
