a mortuary where the goods bee aboue the
value of .xxx.li. and vnder the summe of .xl.
pound the debts payd, that is extortion.
            And if they take of them whose goods amount

to .xl.li. aboue the debts, payd more
then .x.s. for a mortuary: that is extortion.
